Four-body (ZZZZ) interactions

FR-2: Interaction Set Generation

Generate interaction index sets:

G2: two-body terms

G4: four-body terms

Use 0-based indexing

Match analytical loop limits from LABS expansion

FR-3: Quantum Circuit Components
FR-3.1 Two-Qubit Operator Kernel

Implement Pauli-string rotations using:

Basis rotations

RZZ entangling gates

Must support time-dependent coefficients

FR-3.2 Four-Qubit Operator Kernel

Implement structured four-qubit CD block

