Ensure:

One Œ∏ per Pauli string

Clean uncomputation

No residual entanglement

FR-4: Trotterized Time Evolution

Support first-order Trotterization

Apply:

All 2-body terms per step

All 4-body terms per step

Accept time-dependent coefficient schedule

